###
# University Assist API Examples - Cities
# 
# Base URL: https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1
# 
# Replace {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY} with your actual key
# Replace {JWT_TOKEN} with valid JWT for authenticated requests
###

### List all cities
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### List cities with specific columns
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?select=id,name,slug,lat,lng,state
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Search cities by name (case-insensitive)
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?name=ilike.*berlin*
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get cities ordered by name
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?select=id,name,slug&order=name.asc
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get cities with pagination
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?select=id,name,slug&limit=5&offset=0
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get cities with universities count (if supported)
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?select=id,name,slug,universities(count)
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get specific city by slug
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?select=*&slug=eq.berlin
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get cities in specific state
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?select=id,name,slug,state&state=eq.Berlin
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get cities with coordinates for mapping
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?select=id,name,slug,lat,lng&lat=not.is.null&lng=not.is.null
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json

### Full text search in city keywords (if FTS is available)
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.supabase.co/rest/v1/cities?select=id,name,slug,keywords&keywords=cs.{Munich}
apikey: {SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}
Content-Type: application/json